Shakespeare's sonnets,

540
00:42:44,810 --> 00:42:46,350
this is the most famous.

541
00:42:46,430 --> 00:42:47,680
"Sonnet 18."

542
00:42:47,770 --> 00:42:50,020
"Shall I compare thee to a summer's day?"

543
00:42:50,100 --> 00:42:52,150
Published for the first time in 1609.

544
00:42:52,690 --> 00:42:55,900
As you all know,
Shakespeare lived 400 years ago.

545
00:42:55,980 --> 00:43:00,610
As such, there are many archaic phrases
from that time seen in this poem too.

546
