because Seon-u asked me.

552
00:44:17,980 --> 00:44:20,940
But I have no idea
what you'd wanna see me for.

553
00:44:21,650 --> 00:44:24,320
I thought… we could become friends.

554
00:44:25,280 --> 00:44:28,830
