know me at all.

555
00:44:28,910 --> 00:44:30,330
Of course I do!

556
00:44:31,080 --> 00:44:32,200
At the very least,

557
00:44:32,960 --> 00:44:35,370
I know how much
you hate your older sister.

558
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:44,260
Oh.

559
00:44:50,220 --> 00:44:52,680
