Bring Si-u if you can.

560
00:44:52,770 --> 00:44:54,850
-Just ask him yourself.
-You ask him!

561
00:45:02,650 --> 00:45:06,410
Why hasn't Jae-i been in school?
Why isn't she answering my calls?

562
00:45:08,700 --> 00:45:09,950
Did you forget how to talk?

563
00:45:10,030 --> 00:45:11,540
I'm asking you what's going on.

564
00:45:11,620 --> 00:45:13,080
Whatever it is, it's her business.

565
00:45:14,460 --> 00:45:16,830
I don't see any reason
to tell you a thing.

566
00:45:20,750 --> 00:45:22,250
You don't know either, do you?

567
00:45:36,980 --> 00:45:39,400
-She's been banished.
-She what?

568
00:45:39,480 --> 00:45:42,190
