must have said,

572
00:45:48,200 --> 00:45:50,660
"Forget school or anything else,
and get her out of my sight."

573
00:45:50,740 --> 00:45:52,450
She's at their vacation house.

574
00:45:52,530 --> 00:45:55,160
And when she's unbanished?
She'll be sent to New York City.

575
00:45:55,250 --> 00:45:56,370
New York?

576
00:45:56,460 --> 00:45:57,830
Just like that?

577
00:45:57,920 --> 00:46:00,670
Hey, don't you dare go
and tell Ri-an where Jae-i went.

578
00:46:01,590 --> 00:46:02,800
I'm on fire right now.

579
00:46:02,880 --> 00:46:04,420
Get in my way, and I'll destroy you.

580
00:46:04,510 --> 00:46:06,840
