597
00:49:17,320 --> 00:49:20,450
I was worried. I couldn't reach you,
and you weren't even in school.

598
00:49:21,450 --> 00:49:22,870
What are you doing here?

599
00:49:24,910 --> 00:49:28,500
Tell me what's going on.
Tell me what I can do to help you.

600
00:49:33,670 --> 00:49:34,550
Go.

601
00:49:35,800 --> 00:49:37,260
You can't help with anything.

602
00:49:37,340 --> 00:49:39,050
No, I can help.

603
00:49:40,010 --> 00:49:42,890
Whatever it is, it's better
than going through it alone.

604
00:49:46,810 --> 00:49:50,400
Why do you keep pushing me away?
You look like you're about to collapse.

605
00:49:51,020 --> 00:49:52,820
I can tell how much pain you're in.

606
00:49:53,360 --> 00:49:56,110
How do you expect to survive
if you keep shutting me out?

607
00:49:57,820 --> 00:50:00,160
Let go.

608
00:50:00,740 --> 00:50:01,580
No way.

609
00:50:02,660 --> 00:50:05,120
No matter what happens,
I'll stay by your side.

610
00:50:09,120 --> 00:50:11,080
Please just leave me alone!

611
00:50:12,340 --> 00:50:14,090
What can you do for me?

612
00:50:15,460 --> 00:50:18,470
I'm being blackmailed,
and I don't even know who's behind it.

613
00:50:22,720 --> 00:50:23,760
So tell me.

614
00:50:25,020 --> 00:50:26,930
What could you possibly do to help?

615
00:50:31,190 --> 00:50:32,060
Blackmailed?

616
00:50:34,980 --> 00:50:36,190
By who?

617
00:50:38,030 --> 00:50:39,070
And for what?

618
00:50:39,150 --> 00:50:41,110
What could you be blackmailed over?

619
00:50:44,580 --> 00:50:45,740
I killed someone.

620
00:50:53,380 --> 00:50:54,210
What?

621
00:51:00,010 --> 00:51:01,510
I said I killed someone.

622
00:51:11,020 --> 00:51:11,940
Kim Ri-an.

623
00:51:14,730 --> 00:51:16,730
This is a surprise. Why are you here?

624
00:51:17,610 --> 00:51:19,150
I have something to say.

625
00:51:22,070 --> 00:51:25,450
I've thought it over, and this is
the only card I have left to play.

626
00:51:25,530 --> 00:51:27,580
Although, just saying it
isn't really my style.

627
00:51:27,660 --> 00:51:28,580
What card?

628
00:51:31,250 --> 00:51:33,420
Jae-i's off to New York
with Park Seon-jun.

629
00:51:36,000 --> 00:51:37,960
Which means that ship has sailed.

630
00:51:38,050 --> 00:51:41,300
She's at her vacation home. She's gonna
stay there until her move to New York.

631
00:51:44,850 --> 00:51:47,470
So listen carefully
to what I have to say, Kim Ri-an.

632
00:51:48,180 --> 00:51:50,980
It's over between you and her.
You can't stop her from leaving.

633
00:51:54,520 --> 00:51:55,860
Start a new life with me.

634
00:51:59,940 --> 00:52:01,820
I like you, Ri-an.

635
00:52:01,900 --> 00:52:04,410
More than that, I love you.
I have for a long time.

636
00:52:05,120 --> 00:52:06,530
So why don't we make it official?

637
00:52:18,960 --> 00:52:20,010
Jae-i.

638
00:52:21,260 --> 00:52:23,010
You said she's at her vacation house?

